text:
......I think
I'll go with the beef stew...

Oh! Mano!
Does that mean Hiori made it for you!?

Hehe...
Yeah, Hiori-chan made the beef stew for me.
Then I'll have the beef stew too!

Well... The main point was to
introduce a delicious restaurant, right...?

That's true but! Seriously,
it was the most delicious thing I've had recently.

......Maybe it's because we all ate together...
Hiori-chan's cooking was the best too...

I agree that "because we all ate together" but...
Don't praise it too much...
